<!-- wp:button {\\\"className\\\":\\\"is-style-outline\\\"} -->\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-button is-style-outline\\\"><a class=\\\"wp-block-button__link\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/make.wordpress.org\\/core\\/2019\\/09\\/27\\/block-editor-theme-related-updates-in-wordpress-5-3\\/\\\">Lire la suite<\\/a><\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:button --><\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:group -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:group -->\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-group\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-group__inner-container\\\"><!-- wp:image {\\\"align\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"id\\\":37,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\\\"><img class=\\\"wp-image-37\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/twentytwenty\\/assets\\/images\\/2020-three-quarters-4.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3>De Signac \\u00e0 Matisse<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>1er octobre au 1er d\\u00e9cembre<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:button {\\\"className\\\":\\\"is-style-outline\\\"} -->\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-button is-style-outline\\\"><a class=\\\"wp-block-button__link\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/make.wordpress.org\\/core\\/2019\\/09\\/27\\/block-editor-theme-related-updates-in-wordpress-5-3\\/\\\">Lire la suite<\\/a><\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:button --><\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:group --><\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:column --><\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:columns -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"align\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"id\\\":37,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\\\"><img class=\\\"wp-image-37\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/twentytwenty\\/assets\\/images\\/2020-landscape-2.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:group {\\\"align\\\":\\\"wide\\\"} -->\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-group alignwide\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-group__inner-container\\\"><!-- wp:heading {\\\"align\\\":\\\"center\\\",\\\"textColor\\\":\\\"accent\\\"} -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"has-accent-color has-text-color has-text-align-center\\\">\\u00ab\\u00a0Les cyborgs, comme l\\u2019a fait remarquer la philosophe Donna Haraway, ne sont pas respectueux. Ils ne se souviennent pas du cosmos.\\u00a0\\u00bb<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading --><\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:group -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\\\"dropCap\\\":true} -->\\n<p class=\\\"has-drop-cap\\\">Avec ses sept \\u00e9tages d\\u2019architecture remarquable, le E-Mucem pr\\u00e9sente des expositions d\\u2019art contemporain international, parfois accompagn\\u00e9es de r\\u00e9trospectives sur l\\u2019histoire de l\\u2019art. Les questions existentielles, politiques et philosophiques font partie int\\u00e9grante de notre programme. En tant que visiteur, vous \\u00eates invit\\u00e9 \\u00e0 des visites guid\\u00e9es, des conf\\u00e9rences, des projections de films et d\\u2019autres \\u00e9v\\u00e8nements avec entr\\u00e9e gratuite.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Les expositions sont produites par le E-Mucem en collaboration avec des artistes et des mus\\u00e9es du monde entier et attirent souvent l\\u2019attention internationale. Le E-Mucem a re\\u00e7u une mention sp\\u00e9ciale du Mus\\u00e9e europ\\u00e9en de l\\u2019ann\\u00e9e et a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 l\\u2019un des meilleurs candidats pour le Prix du Mus\\u00e9e m\\u00e9diterran\\u00e9en de l\\u2019ann\\u00e9e ainsi que pour le Prix du Mus\\u00e9e du Conseil de l\\u2019Europe.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:group {\\\"customBackgroundColor\\\":\\\"#ffffff\\\",\\\"align\\\":\\\"wide\\\"} -->\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-group alignwide has-background\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #ffffff;\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-group__inner-container\\\"><!-- wp:group -->\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-group\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-group__inner-container\\\"><!-- wp:heading {\\\"align\\\":\\\"center\\\"} -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"has-text-align-center\\\">Devenez membre et obtenez des offres exclusives\\u00a0!<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\\\"align\\\":\\\"center\\\"} -->\\n<p class=\\\"has-text-align-center\\\">Les adh\\u00e9rent\\u00b7es ont acc\\u00e8s \\u00e0 des expositions et des ventes exclusives. Notre abonnement co\\u00fbtent $99.99 et est factur\\u00e9 annuellement.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:button {\\\"align\\\":\\\"center\\\"} -->\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-button aligncenter\\\"><a class=\\\"wp-block-button__link\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/make.wordpress.org\\/core\\/2019\\/09\\/27\\/block-editor-theme-related-updates-in-wordpress-5-3\\/\\\">Rejoignez le club<\\/a><\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:button --><\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:group --><\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<!-- \\/wp:group -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:gallery {\\\"ids\\\":[39,38],\\\"align\\\":\\\"wide\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-gallery alignwide columns-2 is-cropped\\\">\\n<ul class=\\\"blocks-gallery-grid\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"blocks-gallery-item\\\">\\n<figure><img class=\\\"wp-image-39\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/twentytwenty\\/assets\\/images\\/2020-square-2.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-id=\\\"39\\\" data-full-url=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/twentytwenty\\/assets\\/images\\/2020-square-2.png\\\" data-link=\\\"assets\\/images\\/2020-square-2\\/\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\n<\\/li>\\n<li class=\\\"blocks-gallery-item\\\">\\n<figure><img class=\\\"wp-image-38\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/twentytwenty\\/assets\\/images\\/2020-square-1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-id=\\\"38\\\" data-full-url=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/twentytwenty\\/assets\\/images\\/2020-square-1.png\\\" data-link=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/twen